ygData.messageBody:
he conned blue to me at 30, he has some very nasty dot's and dd's, after you
kill him, varsoon the undying will spawn and he will cast darkness spells on
you so dont even think of trying to kite him, and undying hits for 70-80, he
demolished my pet and killed me, because i didnt' meditate long enough after
killing varsoon and his pet. varsoon has about 500 hp i think, his dd did
about 225 damage to me, he only got to cast it once, he casts a fear type
spell i think, not totally sure i resisted it everytime he cast it.

Veldra Rae`lynn
lvl 31 Magician
Veeshan
